## Maintenance Rules

### When to Update:

1. **Start of new phase** - Define THIS phase tasks, create issues, update TASKLIST.md
2. **After completing tasks** - Check off, update progress
3. **When phase complete** - Mark phase âœ…, THEN define next phase
